    "Regarding the contractual forms of authorisation, various scenarios may be envisaged: direct licences, either individually negotiated or publicly offered as standard public licences; collective licences, mandatory licences or even forms of fair compensation.",
    "Regarding direct licences, there appears to be renewed interest in the possibility for authors to individually negotiate a ''right to train'' with AI developers, also thanks to the opt-out provisions of Art.",
